commit.message: Added some better UI functionality
Fixed an error on the welcome class/activity; it's the only update. Also deleted a the library volley since it's never used.

Updating some classes to show a more streamlined process

added to the strings.xml
remove library
Updated the apk packages
Reformatted some values to make sure there weren't any extra decimals.
This commit is to update the apk files.

Further condensation of code for both the Model class and Custom class.
Added more comments for the easier readability of the code.

Added two new drawables for the Welcome class.
Merge remote-tracking branch 'github/master'

Added futher comments, and reworked some bulky methods in the Custom class. Got rid of a bug within the edit texts of the Custom Class

Added popups for the titles within the Custom class to clarify some information to the user. Also added on chart listeners to the bar charts.

Delete AgApp_V2.iml

Not needed, there is already an AgApp.iml

Updated all classes. Removed CustomCornCost and replaced with Custom class; these classes are identical but renamed for easier readability. Removed CornProfit and replaced with Model class; identical but renamed due to eaiser readability.

Added comments to as many different methods as was needed.

Condensed a few methods for faster execution and to have less lines of code

the Custom class is still really dense because it deals with a lot of UI components that are individually handled.

Two new apk's were created with the way the code stands currently.

ImageSliderView removed because it was never used within the scope of the project. Initially it was supposed to help create the sliderview the way it was implemented on the Welcome page, but the library had the necessary methods to create the image slider the way it was intended.
Build gradle and settings gradle for the app were updated to include the AndroidImageSlider library
Updated the Welcome class and its activity to be more readable. Removed unneeded objects and parameters.
deleting image files that are no longer needed. removing these images will hopefully lower size of the project
Deleted ChangeVariables.java per not needed
